<p>The <code>get</code> tag includes a PAD page from the current application.</p>

<h2>Basic Get</h2>
<pre>{open}get 'fragments/hello/hello'{close}</pre>
<p>Included content:</p>
<div style="border:1px solid #ccc; padding:10px;">
{get 'fragments/hello/hello'}
</div>

<h2>Get with Page Index</h2>
<pre>{open}get 'fragments/hello'{close}</pre>
<p>Includes the index page of a directory:</p>
<div style="border:1px solid #ccc; padding:10px;">
{get 'fragments/hello'}
</div>

<h2>Note</h2>
<p>The get tag executes both the .php and .pad files of the included page, making variables from the PHP file available in the template.</p>
